# Core Mechanics

---

## 1. ServerPool

### LRU Algorithm

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[getConnection] --> B{Exists?}
  B -->|Yes| C[Return]
  B -->|No| D{Full?}
  D -->|No| E[Create]
  D -->|Yes| F[Evict oldest]
  F --> E
  E --> G[Return]

  style C fill:#e8f5e9
  style G fill:#e8f5e9
```

### States

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Created
  Created --> InUse
  InUse --> Idle
  Idle --> InUse
  Idle --> Evicted
  Evicted --> [*]
```

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| maxConnections | 6 |
| idleTimeoutMs | 300000 |
| cleanupIntervalMs | 60000 |

---

## 2. Connections

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Disconnected
  Disconnected --> Connecting
  Connecting --> Connected
  Connecting --> Error
  Connected --> Disconnected
```

| Type | Command |
|------|---------|
| Node | `node` |
| Docker | `docker` |
| Python | `uvx` |
| NPX | `npx` |

---

## 3. Tool Cache

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[Request] --> B{Cached?}
  B -->|Yes| C[Return]
  B -->|No| D[Fetch]
  D --> E[Cache]
  E --> F[Return]

  style C fill:#e8f5e9
```

Cache cleared when connection evicted.

