## Error Flow

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[Request] --> B{Valid?}
  B -->|No| C[Error]
  B -->|Yes| D{Server?}
  D -->|No| E[Error]
  D -->|Yes| F{Connect?}
  F -->|No| G[Error]
  F -->|Yes| H[Execute]

  style C fill:#ffcdd2
  style E fill:#ffcdd2
  style G fill:#ffcdd2
```

